title: Another new fave
author: VD
content_html: I’ve seen these cartoons around before, but I didn’t realize that they had a blog. Many of them are quite good; I particularly liked the two that were done after the elimination of the Hamas leader. Check out Cox and Fortnum’s editorial cartoons, if you haven’t already.
